---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import CodeBlock from '../../components/CodeBlock.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Page Content" description="Main content area with App Panel cards for CP.">
  <article class="space-y-12">
    <header class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Page Content</h1>
        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-theme-primary/10 text-theme-primary rounded">CP/VP</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
        The main content area contains stackable App Panel cards - self-contained content containers with toolbars, tabs, and form sections.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- App Panel Overview -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">App Panel Structure</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        Each page can contain one or more App Panel cards. Each panel is a self-contained unit with its own header, toolbar, and content area.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Header Bar (52px)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Title, toolbar buttons (New, Copy, Delete, Attach, Approval), pagination controls, Find input, and Query button.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Tab Strip (42px)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Optional horizontal tabs for sub-sections within the panel (e.g., Basic Info, Details).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Content Area</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Labeled sections with bordered areas, multi-column layouts, form fields, and "Allow Edit" checkboxes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Sub-task Buttons (48px)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Action link buttons at the bottom (Modifications, Revenue Information, Proj Billing Info, etc.).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Visual Example -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Visual Example</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Multiple App Panel cards stacked with 12px gaps between them.</p>
      
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-obsidian p-4 space-y-3 overflow-x-auto">
        <!-- App Panel 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 border-t-[6px] border-t-theme-primary overflow-hidden min-w-[600px]">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="h-[52px] border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm">Manage Project User Flow</span>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-theme-primary text-white rounded">New</button>
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Copy</button>
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Delete</button>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mx-2">1 of 3</span>
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Query</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Top Form Row -->
          <div class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-xs">
              <div>
                <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Project*</label>
                <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">10105</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Name*</label>
                <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Cybersecurity Diag & Mitg</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Abbreviation</label>
                <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"></div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Level</label>
                <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">1</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Tab Strip -->
          <div class="h-[42px] border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 flex items-end gap-1">
            <button class="px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-theme-primary border-b-2 border-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Basic Info</button>
            <button class="px-3 py-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white">Details</button>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Multi-column Sections -->
          <div class="p-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <!-- Section 1: Basic Info -->
              <div class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
                <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Basic Info</span>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Project Classification</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">DIRECT Project</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Project Type</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">GOVSERVICE</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <input type="checkbox" checked class="w-3 h-3 rounded border-slate-300">
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Billable Project</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Section 2: Charging -->
              <div class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
                <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Charging</span>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <input type="checkbox" checked class="w-3 h-3 rounded border-slate-300">
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Active</span>
                    <input type="checkbox" checked class="w-3 h-3 rounded border-slate-300 ml-4">
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Allow Charging</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Account Group</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">GSV</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Section 3: Classification -->
              <div class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
                <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Classification</span>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Owning Org</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">01.01.01</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <input type="checkbox" checked class="w-3 h-3 rounded border-slate-300">
                    <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Default to Owning Organization</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Sub-task Buttons -->
          <div class="h-[48px] border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Modifications</button>
            <span class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600">|</span>
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Revenue Information</button>
            <span class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600">|</span>
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Proj Billing Info</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- App Panel 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 border-t-[6px] border-t-theme-primary overflow-hidden min-w-[600px]">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="h-[52px] border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm">Modifications</span>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-theme-primary text-white rounded">New</button>
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Copy</button>
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Delete</button>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mx-2">1 of 3</span>
              <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Query</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="p-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <!-- Classification Section -->
              <div class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
                <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Classification</span>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div>
                    <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Modification ID</label>
                    <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">10105</div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Start Date</label>
                    <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">04/01/2023</div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">End Date</label>
                    <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">11/30/2025</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Value Modifications -->
              <div class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
                <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Value Modifications</span>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                    <div>
                      <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Value</label>
                      <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-right text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">0.00</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Fee%</label>
                      <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-right text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">0.00%</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-center text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
                    <span>Current</span>
                    <span>Cumulative</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Funding Modifications -->
              <div class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
                <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">Funding Modifications</span>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                    <div>
                      <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Value</label>
                      <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-right text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">0.00</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <label class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Fee%</label>
                      <div class="mt-1 px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded text-right text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">0.00%</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Sub-task Buttons -->
          <div class="h-[48px] border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Award Fee</button>
            <span class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600">|</span>
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Unit Info</button>
            <span class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600">|</span>
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Notes</button>
            <span class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600">|</span>
            <button class="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">ACRN</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Specifications -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Specifications</h2>
      
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Property</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Value</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Notes</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Top border</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">6px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Theme primary color accent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Panel gap</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">12px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Between App Panel cards</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Header height</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">52px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Panel toolbar area</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Tab strip height</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">42px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Optional, below header</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Sub-task height</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">48px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Bottom action buttons</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Section padding</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">16px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Content area padding</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Toolbar button</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">32px height</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">New, Copy, Delete, etc.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Sub-task button</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">24px height</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Link-style text buttons</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Code Example -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Code Example</h2>
      
      <CodeBlock 
        language="html"
        filename="app-panel.html"
        code={`<!-- Page Content Area -->
<main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 space-y-3 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-obsidian">
  
  <!-- App Panel Card -->
  <article class="app-panel bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 
                  border-t-[6px] border-t-theme-primary overflow-hidden">
    
    <!-- Panel Header (52px) -->
    <header class="h-[52px] border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 
                   flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm">Panel Title</h2>
      
      <!-- Toolbar -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <button class="btn-primary px-2 py-1 text-xs">New</button>
        <button class="btn-secondary px-2 py-1 text-xs">Copy</button>
        <button class="btn-secondary px-2 py-1 text-xs">Delete</button>
        
        <!-- Pagination -->
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mx-2">1 of 3</span>
        <button class="btn-secondary px-1.5 py-1"><i class="ti ti-chevron-left"></i></button>
        <button class="btn-secondary px-1.5 py-1"><i class="ti ti-chevron-right"></i></button>
        
        <!-- Find/Query -->
        <input type="text" placeholder="Find" class="w-24 px-2 py-1 text-xs border rounded">
        <button class="btn-secondary px-2 py-1 text-xs">Query</button>
      </div>
    </header>
    
    <!-- Tab Strip (42px, optional) -->
    <nav class="h-[42px] border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 flex items-end gap-1">
      <button class="tab active px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium border-b-2 border-theme-primary">
        Basic Info
      </button>
      <button class="tab px-3 py-2 text-xs text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900">
        Details
      </button>
    </nav>
    
    <!-- Content Area -->
    <div class="p-4">
      <!-- Multi-column Sections -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        
        <!-- Labeled Bordered Section -->
        <section class="relative border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded p-3 pt-4">
          <!-- Floating Label -->
          <span class="absolute -top-2.5 left-3 px-1 text-[10px] font-medium 
                       text-theme-primary bg-white dark:bg-surface">
            Section Label
          </span>
          
          <!-- Section Content -->
          <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <label class="text-slate-500">Field Label</label>
              <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Value</span>
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-3 h-3"> <!-- Allow Edit -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Sub-task Buttons (48px) -->
    <footer class="h-[48px] border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 px-4 
                   flex items-center gap-2">
      <button class="text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Modifications</button>
      <span class="text-slate-300">|</span>
      <button class="text-xs text-theme-primary hover:underline">Revenue Information</button>
    </footer>
    
  </article>
  
  <!-- Additional App Panel Cards... -->
  
</main>`}
      />
    </section>

    <!-- Anatomy -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Anatomy</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-surface rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-border p-6">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-theme-primary text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center font-medium shrink-0">1</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Panel Header</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Contains the panel title on the left, and toolbar buttons, pagination, and query controls on the right. Height: 52px.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-theme-primary text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center font-medium shrink-0">2</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Tab Strip (Optional)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Horizontal tabs for navigating between sub-sections within the panel. Active tab has primary color underline. Height: 42px.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-theme-primary text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center font-medium shrink-0">3</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Labeled Sections</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Content organized into bordered sections with floating labels. Can be single-column or multi-column (2-3 columns) layout.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-theme-primary text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center font-medium shrink-0">4</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Form Fields</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Label-value pairs with optional "Allow Edit" checkboxes. Fields can be inputs, dropdowns, or read-only values.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-theme-primary text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center font-medium shrink-0">5</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Sub-task Buttons</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Link-style buttons at the bottom for navigating to related screens or opening sub-task dialogs. Separated by vertical dividers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Guidelines -->
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Usage Guidelines</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-green-200 dark:border-green-900/50 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            Do
          </h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Use consistent header toolbar layout across panels</li>
            <li>Group related fields into labeled sections</li>
            <li>Provide clear pagination when records exceed one</li>
            <li>Use "Allow Edit" checkboxes for field-level permissions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-red-200 dark:border-red-900/50 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" />
            </svg>
            Don't
          </h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Nest too many panels (keep to 3-4 max per page)</li>
            <li>Overcrowd the toolbar with too many buttons</li>
            <li>Mix different panel styles on the same page</li>
            <li>Hide critical actions in sub-task buttons</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
